    <item>
      <title>保守党前部长称他辞职是因为无法承担抵押贷款加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-29/tory-former-minister-says-he-quit-because-he-could-not-afford-mortgage-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位保守党前部长表示，他去年辞去了这一职务，因为他的部长工资接近 12 万英镑，无法承担不断上涨的抵押贷款还款额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-29/tory-former-minister-says-he-quit-because-he-could-not-afford-mortgage-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 14:37:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗否认参与致命无人机袭击 美国考虑回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/iran-distances-itself-from-us-base-attack-as-biden-urged-to-act</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫表示，正在权衡对周末伊朗支持的武装分子对美国驻约旦基地发动致命袭击的可能反应，华盛顿和德黑兰都试图避免因中东冲突扩大而发生直接对抗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/iran-distances-itself-from-us-base-attack-as-biden-urged-to-act</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 06:48:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着抗议活动的加剧，法国农民封锁了巴黎周边的高速公路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/french-farmers-threaten-to-blockade-paris-as-appeasement-fails</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国农民开始使用拖拉机封锁巴黎周边的高速公路，迫使政府做出进一步让步，以减轻成本上升和繁文缛节的负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/french-farmers-threaten-to-blockade-paris-as-appeasement-fails</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
